///
/// Unknown bugs
@node "Unknown bugs"

  UNKNOWN BUGS:
  =============

  If you get any errors on your computer, please send me an email.

  Please tell me your configuration as exactly as possible:

  - Computer-type
  - OS-version
  - Processor(-card), Coprocessor
  - Chipram / fastram
  - graphic-board
  - Other expansions (cards, drives, cdroms, ...)
  - Versions of used programs and libraries


  Give me an exactly error-description:

  - When did the error occure (... if I do this or that, my machine will do that or this...).
  - Can you avoid the error by doing something ???

  NOTE: I canÇt give any guarantees to an 100% errorfree function of this program !!!

        YOU USE THIS PROGRAM AT YOUR OWN RISK !!!


@endnode
